components.name: CellInputComponent
components.templateData:
<input
  [disabled]="disabled"
  [attr.tabindex]="tabindex"
  [attr.id]="id"
  [attr.class]="isRadio ? 'vds-radio' : 'vds-checkbox'"
  [attr.type]="isRadio ? 'radio' : 'checkbox'"
  (change)="changeEvent.emit($event)"
  (focus)="!disableFocusBlur && !disabled ? handleFocus() : null"
  (blur)="!disableFocusBlur && !disabled ? handleBlur() : null"
  [checked]="checked"
/>
<label
  [attr.for]="id"
  [ngClass]="{
    'vds-radio-label': isRadio,
    'vds-checkbox-label': !isRadio,
    'vds-state--checked': checked ? true : null,
    'vds-state--focus': _isFocused || _isActive ? true : null
  }"
  ><ng-content></ng-content>
</label>

inputsClass.name: checked
inputsClass.description:
Checks the checkbox statically or programmatically.
Use as attribute or input property.
Default: false

inputsClass.name: disabled
inputsClass.description:
Disable checkbox statically or programmatically.
Use as attribute or input property.
Default: false

inputsClass.name: indeterminate
inputsClass.description:
Set indeterminate statically or programmatically.
Use as attribute or input property.
Default: false

inputsClass.name: invalid
inputsClass.description:

components.templateData:
<input
  [attr.checked]="(checked) ? true : null"
  [checked]="(checked) ? true : null"
  [attr.disabled]="(disabled || readOnly) ? true : null"
  [attr.value]="(checkboxValue) ? checkboxValue : null"
  [attr.readOnly]="(readOnly) ? true : null"
  [attr.ariadescribedby]="describedBy"
  [id]="checkboxID"
  [name]="checkboxName"
  (blur)="onBlur()"
  (click)="click()"
  (focus)="onFocus()"
  (keydown.space)="onKeyDown($event)"
  class="vds-checkbox"
  type="checkbox"
  #input
>
<label
  [for]="checkboxID"
  [ngClass]="{
    'vds-checkbox-label': true,
    'vds-state--checked': (checked) ? true : null,
    'vds-state--disabled': (disabled) ? true : null,
    'vds-state--focus': (focused) ? true : null,
    'vds-state--indeterminate': (indeterminate) ? true : null,
    'vds-state--invalid': (invalid) ? true : null
  }"
>
  {{ label }}
</label>

the mini and normal state for side nav.
SidenavToggleButtonComponent can be used in any component that want to
control the side nav
components.templateData:
<button
    class="vds-sidenav-toggle-button"
    [attr.aria-expanded]="!isMini"
    [attr.aria-label]="buttonProps?.ariaLabel ? buttonProps?.ariaLabel : null"
    [attr.tabindex]="buttonProps?.tabIndex ? buttonProps.tabIndex : null"
    (click)="toggle()"
  >
    <vds-icon
      [icon]="isMini ? buttonProps?.closeIcon: buttonProps?.openIcon"
      [tiny]="buttonProps?.iconType === 'tiny' ? true : null"
      [low]="buttonProps?.iconType === 'low' ? true : null"
    >
    </vds-icon>
</button>
